**Mandatory discipline:** Never use `curl https://<live-url>` as an iteration
tool. The live URL is a single-shot post-deploy sanity check, not a verification tool.
On N=2 unsuccessful live curls → `mc blocked` with a question to Boss/{{ operator_name }}, instead of
continuing to go in circles.

### Full-Stack Preview (Tags: backend/api/infra)
```bash
# 1. Worktree + isolated stack
git worktree add /tmp/mc-fullstack-{task-slug} {branch_name}
